Description: Computes propensity score resemblance metrics for comparing
    original and synthetic tabular data. Implements pMSE, SPECKS and PO50,
    together with a wrapper to compute the metrics jointly. The methodology
    follows split-sample evaluation for SPECKS and PO50 to reduce overfitting,
    while pMSE is computed using the full data.
